I introduced Streamlit to my team

and started developing Streamlit-WebRTC
for easier sharing of computer vision demos

"Developing browser-ready real-time computer vision apps with Streamlit"

"Gonna submit talk proposals about
Streamlit-WebRTC to PyCons
where I can have talks in English this year!"

"Real-time browser-ready computer vision apps with Streamlit"

Start the Stlite project:
"Serverless Streamlit" or "In-browser Streamlit"
